Ranger Help for: skin
=====================

SYNTAX:      skin
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     20
SKILL TYPE:  hunting

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to skin a corpse, harvesting useful materials
from a slain creature. The Ranger must have a slash-type weapon wielded
and a corpse present in the room.

Skinning field-dresses the corpse into Ranger survival stores instead
of loose inventory clutter. It can add raw meat to camp stores and
hide scraps or sinew to wildcraft supplies. These materials support
camp cooking, camp tending, make satchel, and other survival work.
